abstract: Bureau of Transportation Statistics says airplanes spent 23 minutes 32 seconds, on average, taxiing between gates and runways in first nine months of 2015.
lead_paragraph: Airplanes spent 23 minutes 32 seconds, on average, taxiing between gates and runways in the first nine months of 2015.
